# Generated / machine-managed artifacts.
#
# These files are auto-generated and MUST stay committed (they are source-of-truth
# the build depends on), but they are large and noisy in diffs. Marking them as
# `linguist-generated` tells GitHub to collapse them in pull-request diffs by
# default and exclude them from repository language statistics.
#
# Do NOT gitignore these:
#   - drizzle `meta/*.json` snapshots are the migration history drizzle-kit diffs
#     against to generate new migrations. Removing them breaks `pnpm db:generate`.
#   - the OpenAPI snapshot is a regression baseline for the snapshot test; without
#     it committed the test can no longer detect unintended API spec changes.

# OpenAPI spec regression snapshot (generated by agents-api/src/__tests__/openapi.test.ts)
agents-api/__snapshots__/openapi.json linguist-generated=true

# Drizzle migration metadata snapshots (managed by drizzle-kit; never edit by hand)
packages/agents-core/drizzle/**/meta/*.json linguist-generated=true
